snippet.title: Garden - Story Gameplay Trailer | Day of the Devs 2021
snippet.description:
A top-down adventure where you play as a little grape named Concord trying to protect and revitalize a struggling community through exploration, crafting and building, making friends, and solving puzzles, coming out this summer.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
